videos.description: Marquette's Theo John works his defender in the paint and sends a nice, behind-the-back bounce pass to Koby McEwen who takes it to the hoop for two.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McEwen takes a sweet dish to the hoop for two) 2020/2/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: McEwen takes a sweet dish to the hoop for two

videos.description: Denzel Mahoney pushes his way through the paint and lays in a tough jumper under pressure in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Mahoney powers Creighton with off-balanced floater) 2020/2/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mahoney powers Creighton with off-balanced floater

videos.description: Koby McEwen lasers a pass to Theo John in the second half who was left wide open for a slam. John then flexes in celebration.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Marquette’s John slams and flexes in celebration) 2020/2/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Marquette's John slams and flexes in celebration

videos.description: Mitch Ballock finds a cutting Marcus Zegarowski as he floats up the to the hoop amid Marquette defenders.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Zegarowski cuts backdoor for a sweet Creighton bucket) 2020/2/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zegarowski cuts backdoor for a sweet Creighton bucket

videos.description: Marcus Zegarowski absorbs contact from Marquette's Markus Howard as they both hit the hardwood, but not before Zegarowski is able to sink a tough layup.
